title: Cream - Wheels of Ice (Tarantura)
description:
Cream
"Wheels of Ice"
San Francisco, California
March 8(10), 1968

Tarantura 2004 - SB 5

Disc 1:

   1. I'm So Glad
   2. Brave Ulysses
   3. Spoonful
   4. Crossroads
   5. We're Going Wrong
   6. Sweet Wine 

Disc 2:

   1. Sunshine of Your Love
   2. N.S.U.
   3. Stepping Out
   4. Traintime
   5. Toad 

Geetarz Comments: 

Nice but incomplete; in its stead I would recommend Graeme Pattingale's excellent 'Live at Winterland' (CRM 917). 

Released as part of the "Cream U.S.A." Boxset.

www.geetarz.org Visitor Comments: 

"I'm not sure I agree with the comment that this set is incomplete. The Cream Remasters "Live at Winterland" set has a bonus track in the form of an alternative mix of "We're Going Wrong," but that doesn't make this set 'incomplete'. This set has the full show, with the exception of "I'm So Glad," which is cut both here and in the Cream Remasters set. - (RM)
